Package com.opengamma.strata.product.swaption

Class PhysicalSwaptionSettlement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.product.swaption.PhysicalSwaptionSettlement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SwaptionSettlement, java.io.Serializable, org.joda.beans.Bean, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean
    public final class PhysicalSwaptionSettlement
extends java.lang.Object
implements SwaptionSettlement, org.joda.beans.ImmutableBean, java.io.Serializable
    Defines the physical settlement type for the payoff of a swaption.

    The settlement type is SettlementType.PHYSICAL. This means that the two parties enter into the actual interest rate swap at the expiry date of the option.
